        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "GREAT BEGINNER GOLD PANNING KIT: This 19pc gold panning kit is a great gold prospecting kit for beginners, as it features a wide selection of gold panning tools to learn and use in the field with; the kit intentionally includes two or more of the hand trowel shovel scoops, gold snifter bottles, gold pans, mesh classifier screens and more, so that new hobbyists can work alongside an experienced partner using the same equipment and learn the tricks of the trade",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ESSENTIAL GOLD MINING PANS & SCREENS: Essential to a new hobbyist or seasoned gold prospector are reliable sifting pans and classifier screens; constructed from heavy-duty plastic, the included riffled pans come in a deep green to help better sift and spot recovered gold flakes or nuggets; the classifier screens feature 304 steel mesh wire that is rust-resistant; and notably, both gold panning tools conveniently fit on the rim of a five gallon bucket for additional sorting",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ROCK PICK HAMMER: A must have if working with any sort of hard bedrock or quartz bearing gold ore, this 20oz hammer features rubberized grip for shock reduction; 11 inches in length and forged from one piece of steel; one side features a square face for hammering rock or driving chisels, while the opposing pointed tip allows you to crack open rocks or hard, dense material",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "POST-RECOVERY CLEAN UP & STORAGE EQUIPMENT: Magnifying tweezers, snifter bottles and glass vials will be convenient to reach for if you're lucky enough to pan some gold, gems or other precious metals; These tools will allow you better to clean, store and examine your newly discovered specimens when on site",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "QUALITY FIELD TESTED DURABLE TOOLS: All the equipment included in this complete gold panning field kit are made from quality material; from the high impact, durable plastic classifier screens and gold pans, to the metal magnifying tweezers and durable magnetic pick-up tool; all the components will see you through many gold prospecting seasons to come",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "ESSENTIAL PROSPECTING EQUIPMENT INCLUDES: This gold prospecting kit comes with three glass screw top gold flake collection vials, two magnifying tweezers, one 10 inch gold pans, two prospectors hand trowels, two large 14 inch finishing gold pans, a black sand magnetic separator pick up tool, three gold suction water tweezers, a 1/2, 1/8 and 1/12 inch mesh classifying screens",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
