        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Outdoor 19pc Ultimate Gold Panning Kit is perfect for beginners, kids, and seasoned prospectors new to or experienced in the hobby. This complete field kit includes essential gold mining tools to help you properly sort, classify, and store recovered gold flakes, gold nuggets, gems, or other precious metals. The kit includes: three glass screw-top gold flake collection vials, two magnifying tweezers, one 10 inch gold pan, two hand trowel prospector's shovel scoops, two large 14 inch finishing gold pans, a black sand magnetic separator pick-up tool, three gold suction water tweezers, and 1/2, 1/8, and 1/12 inch mesh classifying screens. The riffled gold pans are constructed from heavy-duty plastic with a unique riffle design in a deep green color to help better sift and spot gold. The classifier screens feature rust-resistant 304 steel mesh wire and conveniently fit on the rim of a five gallon bucket for additional sorting. A 20oz rock pick hammer with rubberized grip is included for working with hard bedrock or quartz-bearing gold ore. All components are made from quality, field-tested, durable materials designed to last many prospecting seasons. Whether you're panning solo or working alongside an experienced partner, this kit provides everything you need for successful gold prospecting adventures.",
